EN: She made a floral wreath with roses.

ZH: 女孩子们喜欢收到男孩子送的玫瑰花。
EN: Girls like to receive roses from boys.

ZH: 这束玫瑰花很漂亮，我很喜欢。
EN: This bouquet of roses is beautiful, I love it.

